%^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^%^ULINE%^Bones Mystery%^RESET%^

There is an unnatural kinship with the undead, drawing you to them.

%^BOLD%^BLACK%^Revelations:%^RESET%^
( 1) Armor of Bones      : Innate Ability
( 5) Raise the Dead      : Feat to summon a skeleton companion
(10) Near Death          : +2 to saves against disease, poison and mind-affecting spells
(15) Resist Life         : Negative Energy Affinity
(21) Unholy Blood        : Immune to Rend
(31) Final Revelation    : Negative energy damage causes Rend

%^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^Class Skills%^RESET%^: stealth, influence, dungeoneering

%^BOLD%^%^BLACK%^Bonus Spells%^RESET%^: cause fear, false life, animate dead, boneshatter, slay living, circle of death, waves of exhaustion, horrid wilting, wail of the banshee
